stated. 
      1) Extruded Logo Tubes
              What is meant by this?? Does he mean just extrude the logo
      some distance? Or is there something more complicated than that? 
      I just assumed he meant extrude the logo some distance to the back...

      2) Z axis facing backwards.
              Urm...does he mean the Z axis facing backwards relative 
      to the front of the logo? This is what I assumed.

