  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

On Thu, 7 Dec 1995, Mike Vandersommen wrote:

> -> From: Damon L Lacaille <nomad@ALOHA.NET>
> ->
> -> I'm sure this has been asked before - but is there a converter for Li
> -> objects to Imagine?  I used to use PixelPro (I think?) on the Amiga,
> -> been awhile now and don't know of any other programs that will do thi
> -> shareware/pd/commercial - doesn't matter, I just want one - I'll cry
