Here is something that would look good for the 'BLACK HOLE.'  

Since there has been discussion about the gas surrounding the hold I will 
discuss the particles falling into the black hole.

Use particles.  Place a particle source at the location of the black 
hole.  Use emmision and reverse timing to allow the particles to fall 
into the hole.  Use an acceleration of several frames to get the 
particles to move in faster toward the center.  Finally, to simulate the 
spiraling in effect rotate the particle source.

