You can't run Imagine in a DOS session under Win95. In order to run it you have 
to select
Shut Down from the starup menu and then select shut down to DOS prompt. Once at 
the DOS prompt
you can run Imagine just like you used to. When you want to return to Windows ju
st type EXIT
at the DOS prompt. 

