>
>I need some input on color hardcopies of my Imagine renders. I
>currently have an HP 550c, but am not real pleased with the color
>output. I have narrowed my search to the new Epson Color Stylus II
>and the Canon BJC-610. Both boast 720x720 dpi color output on
>plain paper. Anyone have any pros/cons on these two color printers?
