@node IML-381 " MSG-381  Subject: Stage FX, but only once?
@toc contents

Subject: Stage FX, but only once?
Date:    Wednesday, 13 December 1995 08:52:43 
From:    jbk4@email.psu.edu (The Prophet)


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

I tried using stage fx last night and encountered this problem.
I applied ripple once and decided I didn't like it so undo and
reappy.  But the reapply did nothing, if I used the same fx.  If
I switched to, say, shredder, then it would work.  But only once.

As long as I switched from one stage fx to another, it works.  But
if I try repeating the same one consecutively, it doesn't.

I also ran into a phong-error with shredder in detail editor
quickrenders.  Merge didn't help and check object integrity said
it was ok but it wasn't.  I sliced the object and that worked but
it is not a desirable work-around for me.

