@node IML-557 " MSG-557  Subject: IML will LIVE!
@toc contents

Subject: IML will LIVE!
Date:    Saturday, 16 December 1995 12:51:36 
From:    Perry Lucas <plucas@vt.edu>


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

Ladies and Gents,

  I contacted several admin last night to see about relocating
the IML to one of their servers..   About 10 minutes ago, I 
downloaded 100 messages, most of which  were sorry to see 
the IML go.  However, one of those messages buried in the 
gloom was from a Dr. Ben Zenhausern at St. Johns University.

  Hopefully you gathered from this from the title already, but
the IML will live on.  St. Johns will be glad to host the IML on
their server!

  From here, it will take us a few days to set it up, getting the
email addresses set up and contacting respect paries for
different information.  As soon as I have more news, I will post
it.  Hope this alleviates some of your fears about the IML
disappearing.

--Perry Lucas
