@node IML-581 " MSG-581  Subject: So long and thanks for all the fish.
@toc contents

Subject: So long and thanks for all the fish.
Date:    Saturday, 16 December 1995 22:15:27 
From:    Chris Hall <chris.hall@dial.pipex.com>


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

I'd just like to take a moment to thank Dave for his sterling work at
maintaining this list. It is with much dismay that this list is closing. The
mis-adventure of one has spoiled it for the rest of us. Although I was not
very active on the list I enjoy reading it through it's ups and downs and
downright bitchiness now and again. I will miss it and all the characters
that make it what it is now as well as the useful Imagine related info that
