@node IML-604 " MSG-604  Subject: Evading large downloads
@toc contents

Subject: Evading large downloads
Date:    Monday, 18 December 1995 02:57:58 
From:    arandall@direct.ca (alan randall)


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

I've been on this list for only a few days and seem to have arrived just in
time for a flame war of sorts. 

You folks probably already know this, but you can skip big messages like
Imagine 4 code, etc if you're using Eudora. Click on "Special" then
"Switches" and check the box under "Checking" that says, "skip big messages."

Alan Randall


