- On a personal note, I've got the work habits down pat, for dealing 
with the IML within the Pine mail reader. I have much more trouble 
dealing with TRN, which I use to read newsgroups.

- Finally, several members would lose their IML feed because they only 
have mail access to the Net.

Comments?


