Subject: Re[2]: Animation and sound
Date:    Tuesday, 19 December 1995 12:44:40 
From:    spack@mv.us.adobe.com


  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------  

Take a look at Adobe Premiere 4.0.  Supports various compression types, several 

tracks of audio and has nearly 75 effects for wipes, fades, transitions, etc.  
As a bonus, you get TypeOnCall with 220 PS fonts unlocked when registered.  
These fonts are compatible with Imagine.  Also comes with Photoshop LE.  It's 
about $350, which makes it a good deal considering all the extras.

