expense):

IAMTHEABSOLUTEFIRSTTIMEEVERGRANDFIRSTPLACEPRIZEWINNEROFTHEPREMIEREVENTOFTHESUPER
UNOFFICIALIMAGINEMAILINGLIST3DRENDEREDIMAGECONTEST

