++ NOTE ++
This is not a contest to see who the best 3d artist is we have. We have people o
n this list ranging from experienced professionals using 
the latest software and top equipment to people that have just aqquired ver. #2 
without a manual and have much less resources. This 
contest is meant in the spirit of the IML and is meant to be another means of tips, tricks, help, and ideas. All level of users are encour
aged to participate.

++ NOTE 2 ++
As self-appointed ruler of this contest, I have thought this out the best I can.
 While I am sure there are a million ways to improve it, I 
am going to run the first event in a format already determined. You have to star
t somewhere, and once the first one is under way 
we can work on improving the next (if it works at all).


Right after christmas I will post the following:

