directory on aminet.  It contains 19 textures that I have created,
(most of them are old ones), 020.fp and 040.fp(really 040 optimized)
versions are included.

There are 4 new textures:

CSG - Sorta like rendering CSG objects. for ex. objects can
      appear to cut into other objects when rendered.
Lattice - render the faces so that they looks similar to 
