when trying to copy and paste (duplicate and reflect) an object in any of
the editors.

What is the difference between sweep and speen?

Can some one tell me how to use the "Deformation Tool". The manual is not
very explicit on that.

I read in DV magazine, that imagine could not only morph between objects
with the same number of points, but also between diferent objects
(disparate morph) is this true?, 'cause the manual says they have to have
the same number of vertexes.

Thanks in advance!, and hope you understood my best wishes in my last message.
